      "defect_summary": "[workflow_tester][P0] First probe task fails with SessionLockEntry.acquire AttributeError",
      "report_text": "Module: workflow_tester > first real probe task\nSuggested Priority: P0\n\nPhenomenon:\n- A real workflow_tester agent was created on 2026-03-27 and a real chat session was opened: sess-web-20260327-222529-1b13b1.\n- The first real /api/tasks/execute call created task task-20260327-9f356109.\n- The task failed immediately with status=failed and summary=AttributeError: 'SessionLockEntry' object has no attribute 'acquire'.\n- Trace/events show the failure happened before any assistant output was produced.\n\nExpected Result:\n- workflow_tester should be able to execute its first low-risk black-box probe task.\n- The session should produce an assistant result or at least enter normal running/completion flow.\n\nActual Result:\n- The task failed immediately.\n- Backend error: AttributeError: 'SessionLockEntry' object has no attribute 'acquire'.\n\nImpact:\n- The newly created workflow_tester cannot perform the first real bug-probe task.\n- This blocks using workflow_tester as a stable production bug-probing role.\n\nEvidence:\n- D:\\code\\AI\\J-Agents\\Analyst\\.test\\20260327-222226-333\\artifacts\\99-summary.json\n- D:\\code\\AI\\J-Agents\\Analyst\\.test\\20260327-222226-333\\artifacts\\04-task-final.json\n- D:\\code\\AI\\J-Agents\\Analyst\\.test\\20260327-222226-333\\artifacts\\06-task-trace.json\n- D:\\code\\AI\\J-Agents\\Analyst\\.test\\20260327-222226-333\\artifacts\\02-create-session.json",
