        "detail": {
          "text": "After defect process chain execution, new evidence confirms DTS-00001 is still reproducible in the live 8090 runtime.\n\nThe fix node dr-20260327-fc1b947def-fix with run arun-20260327-225945-80da1b ended with failure_reason assignment execution timeout after 1200s at 2026-03-27 23:19:47 +08:00, which blocked release node dr-20260327-fc1b947def-release.\n\nImmediately after that, a fresh black-box retest on http://127.0.0.1:8090 created session sess-web-20260327-232020-a7e191 and task task-20260327-d8b10e5f, and the task still failed with the same backend error: AttributeError: SessionLockEntry object has no attribute acquire.\n\nThis means the production-facing runtime remains broken for workflow_tester first-probe execution.\n\nEvidence:\n- D:/code/AI/J-Agents/Analyst/.test/20260327-231844-225/artifacts/99-summary.json\n- D:/code/AI/J-Agents/Analyst/.test/20260327-232020-167/artifacts/99-summary.json\n- D:/code/AI/J-Agents/Analyst/.test/20260327-232020-167/artifacts/06-task-trace.json"
